{"tid":2508413,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"立會通過入境修例草案，可禁止運載個別乘客，措施將於今年8月1日實施","createTime":"2021-04-28T17:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T21:19:58.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"39b24507db318049b74408f6e82dfc3720353d1b","tid":2508413,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:47:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588259-20210428.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588259-20210428.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzSC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=f8a32059\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1588259-20210428.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=5739b15d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1588259-20210428.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會通過《2020年入境(修訂)條例草案》，賦權保安局局長，可要求航空公司在航班抵港前通報乘客資料，並授權入境處可要求航空公司，禁止運載個別乘客，措施將於今年8月1日實施。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超表示，條例中可指示航機不能運載某人，是針對前來香港，而非離開香港的航機，並不會對香港居民的出入境自由有任何影響，重申《基本法》第三十一條，保障香港居民的旅行和出入境自由。"},{"pid":"47d8f20aa812931aafa7bbff935a020ac31f56b8","tid":2508413,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T18:21:11.000Z","msg":"邊兩位手足仲系議會戰線上堅守緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3e34c23974807eb02359d2db9f7198a953e045f","tid":2508413,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T21:19:58.000Z","msg":"柏林圍牆都話自己係保護牆內居民"}]}